<br />\n台灣唔會無啦啦宣布獨立<br />\n<br />\n但會慢慢走向獨立"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:59:55.000Z","msg":"台灣關係法+台灣旅行法+國防授權法+對台六項保證+台灣安全法(將立) <br />\n<br />\n差唔多相等美國屬土"},{"pid":"44b54f8e35ca073a95b63ae6e184fd4fb636583f","tid":611451,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T07:01:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0052d7ed921867c31dd021a930a1c22d3f982bc9","tid":611451,"uid":68094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T07:03:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4fc37b12d6bec120a14c8835949d4aefb7b555e","tid":611451,"uid":68094,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T07:05:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"035cbe1271e18b54cde483d3567e646473606646","tid":611451,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0052d7ed921867c31dd021a930a1c22d3f982bc9","tid":611451,"uid":68094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1873e2c56e1ab3d425f6d4ff03ad6d9514b3b698","tid":611451,"uid":35790,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c79cdb2e21a6bafd5c886f31cbcfbd1fef1acd47","tid":611451,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:53:01.000Z","msg":"問題大家都知<br />\n台灣唔會無啦啦宣布獨立<br />\n<br />\n但會慢慢走向獨立"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T06:59:55.000Z","msg":"台灣關係法+台灣旅行法+國防授權法+對台六項保證+台灣安全法(將立) <br />\n<br />\n差唔多相等美國屬土"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T07:03:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T07:07:03.000Z","msg":"小心自已後欄著火<br />\n西藏 蒙古 新疆 滿洲 閩粵 香港 大理。。。"}]}